HEADWORD: Radiomicrometer
<hw>Ra`di*o*mi*crom"e*ter</hw>
<pr>(r⟦amac⟧`d⟦icr⟧*⟦osl⟧*m⟦isl⟧*kr⟦ocr⟧m"⟦esl⟧*t⟦etil⟧r)</pr>,
<pos>n.</pos> <ety>[<ets>Radio-</ets> + <ets>micrometer</ets>.]</ety>
<fld>(Physics)</fld> <def>A very sensitive modification or application
